The Cross(V_2, V_4)_d8 piece: bilinear V_2·V_4 from C_4 (deg 4+1+3 = 8;
the (j-1) + (k-1) = 1+3 redistribution among C_4's z-positions).

Using `bch_quartic_term(z, y) = -(1/24)·[y, [z, [z, y]]]`, the bilinear
